description:
The document is a pre-print of the statistical analysis plan and updated protocol for the PRACTISE-trial (Patient-tailored Transcranial Direct Current Stimulation to Improve Stroke Rehabilitation"). The original version of the PRACTISE-trial protocol was published in Trials in 2023.&nbsp; 
 In this updated version of the PRACTISE-trial protocol the overall design is altered to a feasibility- and pilot trial, furthermore a detailed statisitical analysis plan was added. 
 This work was done in collaboration with Copenhagen Trial Unit (CTU), Copenhagen University Hospital Rigshospitalet.&nbsp; 
 The article has been submitted to Heliyon 15th November 2024.

